# Production env injected at Vite build time. Cloudflare Pages overrides
# these via Project Settings -> Environment variables for branch-specific
# values. Keep this file as the canonical "what does the prod build expect?"
# reference.

# Slice 15: same-origin via Cloudflare Pages Function proxy at functions/api/[[path]].ts.
# /api/* on app.practicex.ai is transparently forwarded to api.practicex.ai by
# Cloudflare's edge. Eliminates CORS + cross-origin auth + iframe-PDF issues.
VITE_API_BASE=/api
